<!-- ‡∏ü‡∏≠‡∏£‡πå‡∏°‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏π‡∏•‡∏•‡∏π‡∏Å‡∏Ñ‡πâ‡∏≤ -->
<div class="mt-4 space-y-2">
  <input type="text" id="customerName" placeholder="‡∏ä‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Ñ‡∏∏‡∏ì" class="w-full border rounded px-3 py-2" />
  <input type="text" id="customerAddress" placeholder="‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏≠‡∏¢‡∏π‡πà‡∏à‡∏±‡∏î‡∏™‡πà‡∏á" class="w-full border rounded px-3 py-2" />
  <input type="tel" id="customerPhone" placeholder="‡πÄ‡∏ö‡∏≠‡∏£‡πå‡πÇ‡∏ó‡∏£‡∏®‡∏±‡∏û‡∏ó‡πå" class="w-full border rounded px-3 py-2" />
</div>

<button onclick="checkout()" class="bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 text-white w-full py-2 mt-4 rounded-lg">‡∏™‡∏±‡πà‡∏á‡∏ã‡∏∑‡πâ‡∏≠</button>

      <button onclick="closeCart()" class="absolute top-2 right-2 text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700">‚úñ</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    let cart = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem("cart")) || [];

    function saveCart() {
      localStorage.setItem("cart", JSON.stringify(cart));
    }

    function addToCart(name, price) {
      cart.push({ name, price });
      saveCart();
      updateCartCount();
    }

    function updateCartCount() {
      document.getElementById("cartCount").innerText = cart.length;
    }

   function openCart() {
  const cartItemsDiv = document.getElementById("cartItems");
  cartItemsDiv.innerHTML = "";
  let total = 0;

  if (cart.length === 0) {
    // ‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏°‡∏µ‡∏™‡∏¥‡∏ô‡∏Ñ‡πâ‡∏≤
    cartItemsDiv.innerHTML = `<p class="text-gray-500 text-center">üõí ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏°‡∏µ‡∏™‡∏¥‡∏ô‡∏Ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡πÉ‡∏ô‡∏ï‡∏∞‡∏Å‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤</p>`;
  } else {
    // ‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏µ‡∏™‡∏¥‡∏ô‡∏Ñ‡πâ‡∏≤ ‡πÅ‡∏™‡∏î‡∏á‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£
    cart.forEach((item, index) => {
      total += item.price;
      const div = document.createElement("div");
      div.className = "cart-item flex justify-between items-center bg-gray-100 p-2 rounded";
      div.innerHTML = `
        <span>${item.name}</span>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span>‡∏ø${item.price}</span>
          <button onclick="removeFromCart(${index})" class="text-red-500 hover:text-red-700">üóëÔ∏è</button>
        </div>
      `;
      cartItemsDiv.appendChild(div);
    });
  }

  document.getElementById("cartTotal").innerText = "‡∏ø" + total;
  document.getElementById("cartModal").classList.remove("hidden");
}


    function closeCart() {
      document.getElementById("cartModal").classList.add("hidden");
    }

    function removeFromCart(index) {
      cart.splice(index, 1);
      saveCart();
      openCart();
      updateCartCount();
    }

    function checkout() {
  const name = document.getElementById("customerName").value.trim();
  const address = document.getElementById("customerAddress").value.trim();
  const phone = document.getElementById("customerPhone").value.trim();

  if (!name || !address || !phone) {
    alert("‡∏Å‡∏£‡∏∏‡∏ì‡∏≤‡∏Å‡∏£‡∏≠‡∏Å‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏π‡∏•‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏ö‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏ß‡∏ô‡∏Å‡πà‡∏≠‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏≥‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏™‡∏±‡πà‡∏á‡∏ã‡∏∑‡πâ‡∏≠");
    return;
  }

  // ‡∏™‡πà‡∏á‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏π‡∏•‡πÑ‡∏õ‡∏¢‡∏±‡∏á backend ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠‡πÅ‡∏™‡∏î‡∏á‡∏ú‡∏•
  alert(`‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏ö‡∏Ñ‡∏∏‡∏ì‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏™‡∏±‡πà‡∏á‡∏ã‡∏∑‡πâ‡∏≠!\n\n‡∏ä‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠: ${name}\n‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏≠‡∏¢‡∏π‡πà: ${address}\n‡πÄ‡∏ö‡∏≠‡∏£‡πå‡πÇ‡∏ó‡∏£: ${phone}`);

  // ‡∏•‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏ï‡∏∞‡∏Å‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤
  cart = [];
  saveCart();
  closeCart();
  updateCartCount();

  // ‡∏•‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏ü‡∏≠‡∏£‡πå‡∏°
  document.getElementById("customerName").value = "";
  document.getElementById("customerAddress").value = "";
  document.getElementById("customerPhone").value = "";
}


    function showCategory(category, button) {
      // ‡∏ã‡πà‡∏≠‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏∏‡∏Å‡∏´‡∏°‡∏ß‡∏î‡∏´‡∏°‡∏π‡πà
      document.querySelectorAll('.grid').forEach(el => el.classList.add('hidden'));
      // ‡πÅ‡∏™‡∏î‡∏á‡∏´‡∏°‡∏ß‡∏î‡∏´‡∏°‡∏π‡πà‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏Å
      document.getElementById(category).classList.remove('hidden');

      // ‡πÄ‡∏õ‡∏•‡∏µ‡πà‡∏¢‡∏ô‡∏™‡∏µ‡∏õ‡∏∏‡πà‡∏°
      document.querySelectorAll('button').forEach(btn => btn.classList.remove('bg-opacity-75'));
      button.classList.add('bg-opacity-75');
    }

   
   updateCartCount();
   document.getElementById("cartBtn").addEventListener("click", openCart);
  function filterItems() {
  const query = document.getElementById("searchInput").value.toLowerCase();
  const allMenus = document.querySelectorAll('.grid > div');

  allMenus.forEach(item => {
    const name = item.querySelector('h4')?.innerText.toLowerCase() || "";
    if (name.includes(query)) {
      item.classList.remove("hidden");
    } else {
      item.classList.add("hidden");
    }
  });
}

  </script>
